data.description: Ever dreamed of having a pool INSIDE your home?  Well, this charming 3 bedroom/2 bathroom/ 2,216 sqft home conveniently located between South Boston and Clarksville VA has it! This unique home features a open floor plan with over sized rooms, including a 30' x 16'6 Den, 35' x 54' indoor pool, THREE car garage, wood stove, fireplace and a fenced in back yard!  A extra large Taylor water stove to heat the pool and hot water in home  (if preferred)  RECENT UPDATES & UPGRADES: METAL ROOF 2020 / Trane HEAT PUMP 2021 / FLOORING 2019 / WELL PUMP & HOT WATER TANK 2020
